.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JG49P0v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJG49P0v.jpg&h=bfdca82e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標一、哂馬</span></strong></span><br />\n由於警狗唔再批不反，即使批左亦會製造衝突。<br />\n為左令和理非可以舒舒服服地出返黎，展示人數同民意，<br />\n所以就利用黃店門外既人龍，製造畫面同話題吸引媒體注意。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">目標二、支持黃色經濟</span></span></strong><br />\n依幾個月生意難免受影響，加上可能被藍絲杯葛，<br />\n良心黃店係好需要大家支持。<br />\n最實際既支持當然就係拎銀包出黎，入錢入錢入錢！<br />\n另外參考連登既食評，由於良心經營既關係，黃店食物質素一般都偏高，<br />\n絕對係win win雙贏！<br />\n<br />\n------------國際文宣------------<br />\n請將買返黎既貨物/食物同排隊盛況<br />\n一齊用<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#Buy4HK</span></span></strong><br />\n放上IG, Twitter, reddit"},{"pid":"1fc1ac22ca3b4b38c74a5def4e4628294d578887","tid":1634261,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T08:34:31.000Z","msg":"勁推<br />\n<br />\n義士既血不能白流 <br />\n<br />\n香港人退無可退 只能反抗<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"e029f6a5dee2928c026657964ebdc2578239a7ea","tid":1634261,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T11:13:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">黨鐵大大點死都死掂比你地開工開市架啦 </span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: violet;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你班奴隸 聽日準時迫黨鐵返工啦</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"40ecda945bef52af14f66ce14a7b75d155247370","tid":1634261,"uid":212961,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0